rows.label: qst720403_msg0001
rows.name: Welcome back!

rows.label: qst720403_msg0002
rows.name:
We managed to get all the food you
wanted. Take a look!

rows.label: qst720403_msg0003
rows.name: I'll take the liberty of confirming...

rows.label: qst720403_msg0004
rows.name:
Three Grimdark Crabs,
five portions of Feris Beastmeat...

rows.label: qst720403_msg0005
rows.name:
Three Lactonuts, and
seven measures of Weeping Flour...

rows.label: qst720403_msg0006
rows.name:
Oh! There appears to be even more
here than I originally requested!

rows.label: qst720403_msg0007
rows.name:
Think of it as a little token of our
appreciation, Ivan!

rows.label: qst720403_msg0008
rows.name:
Also, if you make yourself ill eating
rotten food, it's going to affect the
troops' morale.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0009
rows.name:
So be sure to eat your fill of this
stuff, and keep up the good work!

rows.label: qst720403_msg0010
rows.name: Y-Your Highness!

rows.label: qst720403_msg0011
rows.name:
I'm scarcely worthy of such an honor!
With this, my devotion is sealed
forever!

rows.label: qst720403_msg0012
rows.name: Hey. Come on. Don't go overboard.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0013
rows.name:
Adel-sama! Would you mind if
me and Sata took care of the cooking
today?

rows.label: qst720403_msg0014
rows.name: The two of you?

rows.label: qst720403_msg0015
rows.name: Yup.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0016
rows.name:
The caterers are looking pretty
overworked since all the other people
showed up. We should help out.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0017
rows.name: That's very thoughtful of you.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0018
rows.name:
Then, I'd be honored to ask for your
assistance.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0019
rows.name: OK! Let's get to it Sata!

rows.label: qst720403_msg0020
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Hmmm... This is good, but it's only a
temporary measure.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0021
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]I need to come up with a permanent
solution...
